title: SumSoc a very active League of Legends group in oce!
body:
Hello Summoners,

Just wanted to let you know about Summoners Society. We are 3rd largest but most active league of legends group in OCE.

We run monthly tournaments.
Solo/duo (Sign as a solo or duo and get put on a team)
Premade 5v5s
We also run weekly customs.

We also do a  lot of other things. So feel free to come check us out.

Our facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/SummonersSocietyOCE/ 
(If your fb is less then one year old or doesn't say where you live, just let us your facebook name and we will let you in!)

Our discord: https://discord.gg/p2QkBzH

replies.body: the discord is where i hang out
